            "title": "港股跌102點  首掛兩新股大瀉",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌102點或0.4%，報25833 ; 恒生科技數開報5592，跌23點或0.41% ; 恒生國企指數開報9077，跌29點或0.32%。    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交25.99億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"天域半導體招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02658.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"天域半導體招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02658.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">天域半導體招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">天域半導體(02658)首掛，較招股價低34.48% ; 遇見小麵(02408)挫28.98%，報5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)跌1.14%，報552.5元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)跌0.78%，報153.2元。網易(09999)跌0.92%，報215.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創科實業(00669)跌2.21%，報93元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國太保(02601)趺0.95%，報31.42元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">碧桂園(02007)升1.96%，報0.52元，9 筆境內債券重組通過。</p>\n</div>",
